# Changelog for lovstudio/fix

## v1.1.0 - 2025-12-21
- Migrated fix commands to lovstudio/fix/ namespace
- fix.md → lovstudio/fix/fix.md
- fix-by-add-log.md → lovstudio/fix/by-add-log.md
- fix-until-no-error.md → lovstudio/fix/until-no-error.md

## v1.0.0 - 2025-01-25 (fix.md)
- Initial version of error diagnosis and fixing assistant
- Implements comprehensive error analysis workflow
- Supports various error types (syntax, runtime, configuration, dependencies)

## v1.0.0 - 2025-11-29 (by-add-log.md)
- Initial version
- 支持多语言日志格式（JS/TS、Python、Go）
- 策略性日志添加流程

## v1.0.0 - 2025-10-16 (until-no-error.md)
- Automated error fixing loop until success
- Incremental validation and root cause focus
- Infinite loop prevention mechanism

